summary: This is an email from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation and Trafficking team regarding digital evidence from the Miami investigation. It includes attachments with evidence inventory spreadsheets for digital items.

events.title: Miami Digital Evidence Inventory Email
events.description: FBI New York Field Office sends email with attached spreadsheets containing inventory of Miami digital evidence items from the scan project.

keyFacts: The FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation and Trafficking team is handling digital evidence from Miami.
There was a 'scan project' that inventoried Miami digital evidence items.
Two spreadsheets are referenced: MM-108062 Evidencein Digitabdsx and MM-108062_Miami_Evidenceinventory.xlsx.
The email demonstrates ongoing evidence management in the investigation.
No specific individuals are named in this document.
